      "credentials": {
        "googleSheetsOAuth2Api": { "id": "google-sheets", "name": "Google Sheets" }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gemini-2.5-flash",
        "options": { "temperature": 0.6, "maxOutputTokens": 2048 },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Generate a comprehensive weekly review for Vishal.\n\nThis week's data:\n\nTodos:\n{{ $('Read Todos (Weekly)').all().slice(-30).map(t => `${t.json.date}|${t.json.task}|${t.json.status}|${t.json.priority}`).join('\\n') }}\n\nWorkouts:\n{{ $('Read Workouts (Weekly)').all().slice(-7).map(w => `${w.json.date}|${w.json.type}|${w.json.duration_min}min|${w.json.distance_km}km`).join('\\n') }}\n\nFinance:\n{{ $('Read Transactions (Weekly)').all().slice(-30).map(t => `${t.json.date}|${t.json.category}|${t.json.amount}|${t.json.merchant}`).join('\\n') }}\n\nCreate a weekly review that:\n1. *Productivity*: Task completion rate, patterns, wins\n2. *Fitness*: Workouts done vs target (3 runs, 15km/week), trends\n3. *Finance*: Week's spending, budget adherence, notable expenses\n4. *Health*: Nutrition patterns, sleep, activity\n5. *Top 3 Wins* of the week\n6. *Top 2 Improvements* needed\n7. *Next Week's Focus*: 3 specific, actionable goals\n8. *Comparison*: vs last week (better/worse/same)\n\nBe honest but encouraging. Use data to back up observations.\nEnd with a motivational close.\nFormat for Telegram Markdown."
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "weekly-review",
      "name": "Generate Weekly Review",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [700, 560],
      "credentials": {
        "googleGeminiApi": { "id": "gemini-api", "name": "Gemini API" }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "={{ $env.TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID }}",
        "text": "={{ $json.text }}",
        "additionalFields": { "parse_mode": "Markdown" }
      },
      "id": "send-weekly",
      "name": "Send Weekly Review",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [940, 560],
      "credentials": {
        "telegramApi": { "id": "telegram-bot", "name": "Mitra Telegram Bot" }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "documentId": { "__rl": true, "mode": "id", "value": "={{ $env.SPREADSHEET_ID }}" },
        "sheetName": { "__rl": true, "mode": "name", "value": "Weekly_Summary" },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "week_start": "={{ new Date(Date.now() - 7*24*60*60*1000).toISOString().split('T')[0] }}",
            "ai_summary": "={{ $json.text.substring(0, 500) }}"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "save-weekly",
      "name": "Save Weekly Summary",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
